research_municipality_step.notes: Palestine, TX operates under a Mayor-Council form of government, consisting of a Mayor elected at large and six Council Members elected by district for two-year terms. The May 3, 2025, election results indicate Ava Harmon won the District 2 seat. Mitchell Jordan was re-elected Mayor in May 2025. Kenneth Davidson (District 4) and Christopher Gibbs (District 6) were also re-elected in May 2025.
